# LeakSanitizer suppressions for the decompiler memory-leak harness.
#
# Anything matched here is reported as a "suppressed leak" and the harness
# still exits zero.  Keep the list short and well-justified: every entry
# represents memory we have inspected and consciously decided not to fix
# in this round.
#
# At present the harness reports zero leaks on the base branch, so this
# file exists only as scaffolding for follow-up work (e.g. once additional
# scenarios are added that may surface known leaks in third-party libs).
